{"title":"EASYHOOK","date":"2022-01-28T14:53:57.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2022年1月28日","L":"2022/01/28","MM-DD":"01-28"},"link":"2022/01/28/EASYHOOK","tags":["HOOK"],"categories":["Reverse"],"updated":"2022-01-28T08:14:23.162Z","content":"<h2 id=\"解题思路\">解题思路<a title=\"#解题思路\" href=\"#解题思路\"></a></h2>\n<p>第一次接触HOOK类的题目，虽然做了很久也看了别的师傅的WP，但也算有所收获</p>\n<p>首先用IDA打开文件</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/EASYHOOK/EASYHOOK0.png\" alt=\"随便写写\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>刚开始我就卡了好久，直接看那个sub_401240假验证函数了</p>\n<p>其实这个函数啥也不是（其实看到This_is_not_the_flag这个字符串我就应该回头了，但是我头太铁了）</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/EASYHOOK/EASYHOOK1.png\" alt loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>后来看了师傅的WP才知道关键在<strong>sub_401220</strong>函数（PS:师傅WP地址<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/CSNN2019/article/details/113855901\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.csdn.net/CSNN2019/article/details/113855901</a>）</p>\n<p>分析一下这个函数</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/EASYHOOK/EASYHOOK2.png\" alt loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>这四句代码将<strong>WriteFile</strong>在<strong>kernel32.dll</strong>中的地址拿了出来赋值给了<strong>WriteFile_0</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">v2 = GetCurrentProcessId();</span><br><span class=\"line\">hProcess = OpenProcess(<span class=\"number\">0x1F0FFF</span>u, <span class=\"number\">0</span>, v2);</span><br><span class=\"line\">v0 = LoadLibraryA(LibFileName);</span><br><span class=\"line\">*(_DWORD *)WriteFile_0 = GetProcAddress(v0, ProcName);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/EASYHOOK/EASYHOOK3.png\" alt loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>继续分析下面代码</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">lpAddress = *(LPVOID *)WriteFile_0;<span class=\"comment\">//将**WriteFile**在**kernel32.dll**中的地址给IpAddress</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> ( !*(_DWORD *)WriteFile_0 )</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> sub_401370((<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>)aApi);<span class=\"comment\">//这两句时提示获取WriteFile地址失败，这里没有实际用处</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>下面这两句代码将<strong>WriteFile</strong>在<strong>kernel32.dll</strong>中的地址的前五个字节存在<strong>unk_40C9B4</strong>（PS:如果看不懂这两句可以直接去看汇编，因为五个字节要分一个<strong>dword</strong>和一个<strong>byte</strong>来赋值，所以有两句**）**</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">unk_40C9B4 = *(_DWORD *)lpAddress;</span><br><span class=\"line\">*((_BYTE *)&amp;unk_40C9B4 + <span class=\"number\">4</span>) = *((_BYTE *)lpAddress + <span class=\"number\">4</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>这两句代码将一个完整的跳转指令<strong>call sub_401080</strong>的字节码赋值在了地址<strong>0x40C9BC</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">byte_40C9BC = <span class=\"number\">0xE9</span>;<span class=\"comment\">//0xE9是call指令的字节码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> dword_40C9BD = (<span class=\"keyword\">char</span> *)sub_401080 - (<span class=\"keyword\">char</span> *)lpAddress - <span class=\"number\">5</span>;<span class=\"comment\">//跳转的目的地址- 跳转的起始地址- 指令长度</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/EASYHOOK/EASYHOOK4.png\" alt loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>然后最后返回时调用了<strong>sub_4010D0</strong>函数</p>\n<p>可以看到这个函数的作用就是将原本<strong>WriteFile</strong>在<strong>kernel32.dll</strong>中的地址的前五个字节改写成了<strong>call sub_401080</strong>这个5字节的指令，从而在调用<strong>WriteFile</strong>就会执行这条指令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">return</span> sub_4010D0();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">BOOL <span class=\"title\">sub_4010D0</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  DWORD v1; <span class=\"comment\">// [esp+4h] [ebp-8h] BYREF</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  DWORD flOldProtect; <span class=\"comment\">// [esp+8h] [ebp-4h] BYREF</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  v1 = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  VirtualProtectEx(hProcess, lpAddress, <span class=\"number\">5u</span>, <span class=\"number\">4u</span>, &amp;flOldProtect);</span><br><span class=\"line\">  WriteProcessMemory(hProcess, lpAddress, &amp;byte_40C9BC, <span class=\"number\">5u</span>, <span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> VirtualProtectEx(hProcess, lpAddress, <span class=\"number\">5u</span>, flOldProtect, &amp;v1);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>再回到原来处，可以看到在14行调用了<strong>WriteFile</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/EASYHOOK/EASYHOOK5.png\" alt loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>接下来分析<strong>sub_401080</strong>函数</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> __stdcall <span class=\"title\">sub_401080</span><span class=\"params\">(HANDLE hFile, LPCVOID lpBuffer, DWORD nNumberOfBytesToWrite, LPDWORD lpNumberOfBytesWritten, LPOVERLAPPED lpOverlapped)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> v5; <span class=\"comment\">// ebx</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  v5 = sub_401000((<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>)lpBuffer, nNumberOfBytesToWrite);<span class=\"comment\">// 真验证函数</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  sub_401140();                                 <span class=\"comment\">// 还原WriteFile在kernel32.dll中的地址</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  WriteFile(hFile, lpBuffer, nNumberOfBytesToWrite, lpNumberOfBytesWritten, lpOverlapped);<span class=\"comment\">// 还原后再执行一遍保证了WriteFile指令的执行</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> ( v5 )</span><br><span class=\"line\">    *lpNumberOfBytesWritten = <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>所以只需要看<strong>sub_401140</strong>函数分析即可</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> __cdecl <span class=\"title\">sub_401000</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> a1, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> a2)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">char</span> i; <span class=\"comment\">// al</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">char</span> v3; <span class=\"comment\">// bl</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">char</span> v4; <span class=\"comment\">// cl</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> v5; <span class=\"comment\">// eax</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> ( i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; a2; ++i )</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> ( i == <span class=\"number\">18</span> )</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      *(_BYTE *)(a1 + <span class=\"number\">18</span>) ^= <span class=\"number\">0x13</span>u;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> ( i % <span class=\"number\">2</span> )</span><br><span class=\"line\">        v3 = *(_BYTE *)(i + a1) - i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">else</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        v3 = *(_BYTE *)(i + a1 + <span class=\"number\">2</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">      *(_BYTE *)(i + a1) = i ^ v3;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  v4 = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> ( a2 &lt;= <span class=\"number\">0</span> )</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  v5 = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> ( byte_40A030[v5] == *(_BYTE *)(v5 + a1) )</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    v5 = ++v4;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> ( v4 &gt;= a2 )</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/01/28/EASYHOOK/EASYHOOK6.png\" alt loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"解密代码\">解密代码<a title=\"#解密代码\" href=\"#解密代码\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span><span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;cstring&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">char</span> old[] =</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"number\">97</span>, <span class=\"number\">106</span>, <span class=\"number\">121</span>, <span class=\"number\">103</span>, <span class=\"number\">107</span>, <span class=\"number\">70</span>, <span class=\"number\">109</span>, <span class=\"number\">46</span>, <span class=\"number\">127</span>, <span class=\"number\">95</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"number\">126</span>, <span class=\"number\">45</span>, <span class=\"number\">83</span>, <span class=\"number\">86</span>, <span class=\"number\">123</span>, <span class=\"number\">56</span>, <span class=\"number\">109</span>, <span class=\"number\">76</span>, <span class=\"number\">110</span>, <span class=\"number\">0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">char</span> flag[<span class=\"number\">19</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    old[<span class=\"number\">18</span>] ^= <span class=\"number\">19</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> ( i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; <span class=\"number\">19</span>; ++i )</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> ( i == <span class=\"number\">18</span> )</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">else</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            old[i] ^= i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> ( i % <span class=\"number\">2</span> )</span><br><span class=\"line\">                flag[i] = old[i] + i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">else</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                flag[i + <span class=\"number\">2</span>] = old[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//                v3 = *(_BYTE *)(i + a1 + 2);</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//            *(_BYTE *)(i + a1) = i ^ v3;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;%s&quot;</span>,flag);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//flag&#123;Ho0k_w1th_Fun&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>逆向之路漫漫，同志仍需努力</p>\n","prev":{"title":"OsStart","link":"2022/01/28/OsStart"},"plink":"https://bexh0lder.github.io/2022/01/28/EASYHOOK/","toc":[{"id":"解题思路","title":"解题思路","index":"1"},{"id":"解密代码","title":"解密代码","index":"2"}],"copyright":{"custom":"转载请标明作者:D"},"reading_time":"896 字约 6 分钟"}